    <!-- Tips Section -->
    <section class="tips">
        <h2>Healthy Lifestyle Tips</h2>
        <div class="tips-container">
            <div class="tip">Hydrate regularly with at least 8-10 glasses of water daily</div>
            <div class="tip">Incorporate 30 minutes of physical activity 5-6 days weekly</div>
            <div class="tip">Prioritize 7-9 hours of quality sleep nightly in a dark, cool room</div>
            <div class="tip">Practice mindful eating by chewing slowly and removing distractions</div>
            <div class="tip">Drastically reduce processed foods and added sugars</div>
            <div class="tip">Meal prep nutritious options to avoid unhealthy convenience foods</div>
            <div class="tip">Include a lean protein source at each meal</div>
            <div class="tip">Fill half your plate with non-starchy vegetables</div>
            <div class="tip">Choose whole grains over refined carbohydrates</div>
            <div class="tip">Incorporate healthy fats like avocados, nuts, and olive oil</div>
            <div class="tip">Track your food intake to increase awareness of eating habits</div>
            <div class="tip">Read nutrition labels carefully to identify hidden sugars/fats</div>
            <div class="tip">Practice stress management techniques like meditation</div>
            <div class="tip">Limit alcohol consumption to recommended guidelines</div>
            <div class="tip">Include probiotics for gut health through yogurt/kefir</div>
            <div class="tip">Vary your protein sources throughout the week</div>
            <div class="tip">Stock your kitchen with healthy staples to enable better choices</div>
            <div class="tip">Use herbs and spices instead of excessive salt for flavor</div>
            <div class="tip">Never skip breakfast to prevent overeating later</div>
            <div class="tip">Practice proper portion control using smaller plates</div>
            <div class="tip">Allow occasional treats to prevent feelings of deprivation</div>
            <div class="tip">Stay active throughout the day beyond just workouts</div>
            <div class="tip">Monitor cholesterol and blood pressure regularly</div>
            <div class="tip">Get annual physical exams and blood work</div>
            <div class="tip">Focus on fiber for digestion and satiety (25-35g daily)</div>
            <div class="tip">Choose organic when possible to limit pesticide exposure</div>
            <div class="tip">Cook more meals at home to control ingredients</div>
            <div class="tip">Practice gratitude to improve mental well-being</div>
            <div class="tip">Socialize regularly to support emotional health</div>
            <div class="tip">Take time for hobbies and relaxation daily</div>
            <div class="tip">Gradually implement changes for sustainable habits</div>
            <div class="tip">Celebrate small victories in your health journey</div>
            <div class="tip">Consult professionals for personalized nutrition plans</div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
